Package de.mvise.iqm4hd.dsl.parser.gen

Interface IQM4HDParserListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IQM4HDParserBaseListener
    public interface IQM4HDParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by IQM4HDParser.
